Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.90,0:00:11.24,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.99,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:18.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:26.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:30.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:33.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.92,0:00:36.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:40.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:54.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.17,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:02.66,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,140.389)}The Mount Rokko Pursuit of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(487.167,690.389)}the Monstrous Abugomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.72,0:01:29.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kobe is the largest\Nharbor in Western Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:31.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The FBI caught word of Shocker\Noperating here in Kobe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.62,0:01:35.81,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and sent Hongo Takeshi and Taki\NKazuya to fly secretly to Western Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:38.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and investigate Shocker's activities there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.58,Italics,,0,0,0,,I trailed him here from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.58,0:03:03.71,Italics,,0,0,0,,This time, I'll find evidence\Ntying him to Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.48,0:03:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an FBI inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I applaud your efforts to track me\Nall the way from Mexico.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.72,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... you knew I was tracking you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're a Shocker liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.69,0:03:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's leading electronic\Nengineer, Doctor Kihara Michitoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is staying at the Arima Hot Springs\Nfor an academic conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to bring Doctor Kihara into\Nthe fold as a Shocker scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring Doctor Kihara, that Nobel\NPrize frontrunner, into Shocker?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.13,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no mere Shocker liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a venomous horsefly cyborg\Nborn deep in the Mexican jungles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The venomous horsefly that\Ncan kill a cow with one sting?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They call me Abugomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've told you my identity and my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to die now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.10,0:04:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's what's going\Nto happen, FBI scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.47,0:05:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go! Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.49,0:05:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker cyborg...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! I'll send you to join\Nthat friend of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,George?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.98,0:05:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed George?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.04,0:05:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, take the child to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.03,0:05:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- I'll face you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.48,0:06:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here to get your\Nmeasure this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.98,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The next time we meet, you will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Abugomes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Letting yourself be distracted\Nby such nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the child you let\Nescape heard everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you be sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.10,0:06:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If Kamen Rider learns of our plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll have trouble on our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.65,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish off the child that\NAbugomes let escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we finish off the Kamen Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need you to tell me these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides... defeating Rider\Nwill require some planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:07:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's all the luggage for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a trip to Western Japan,\Nnot a world cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.81,0:07:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it's not far, it's still a trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to impress Mr. Hongo and Mr. Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.25,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold this, would you, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! The bus is about to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.20,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's very comfortable,\Nand the scenery is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No complaints here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.48,0:07:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or so I'd like to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're still stuck with the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.52,0:07:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me for being old!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.68,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking a ten-minute breather here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be the Tachibana Tobei party?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,An acquaintance of yours\Nis waiting on the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's Hongo and Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tachibana Tobei. You won't\Nbe getting back on that bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.29,0:08:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will take you the rest of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them to Shocker's\NWestern Japan Branch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:24.39,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs50}Kasuga Surgical Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.29,0:08:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Abugomes nearly killed this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means she must know\Nsomething important about Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama, I'm scared. I'm scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.84,0:08:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Cathy, you're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left to be afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.20,0:09:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember what that monster said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.94,0:09:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a good girl, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell us, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.13,0:09:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they were going\Nto bring a doctor into Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he mention his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.65,0:09:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to remember. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, take Cathy to safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.63,0:09:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hongo!\N- That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.26,0:09:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Kihara! He said Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You handle things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.58,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you... the next\Ntime we met, I would finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.09,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen carefully... Shocker\Nhas your friends in custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.52,0:11:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to see them\Ndead, you'd better not move.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.51,0:11:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.01,Italics,,0,0,0,,Abugomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:19.46,Italics,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kihara is at the Arima\NHot Springs hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.46,0:11:22.21,Italics,,0,0,0,,Go kidnap him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:34.70,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:38.98,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs55}National Park Arima Hot Springs
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.25,0:11:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to meet one of\Nyour residents: Doctor Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He's out for a walk in Zuihoji\NPark at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Zuihoji Park?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.83,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.46,0:12:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Doctor Kihara?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.81,0:12:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interested in putting\Nyour amazing brain to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My brain, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker is working on a\Npowerful radio wave scrambler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We need your electronic\Nengineering skills to complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.01,0:12:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A radio wave scrambler, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker will block all communications
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and alter them to suit our own purposes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It will throw Japan into chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd never go along with something so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.10,0:13:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.26,0:13:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth and come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.82,0:13:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see that, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.80,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I certainly dodged a bullet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't realize they've taken a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But what will happen to\Nthe young man taking my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to infiltrate\NShocker's Western Japan base
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.57,0:14:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and rescue our captured colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.61,Italics,,0,0,0,,I've learned Shocker's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:25.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,Now I just need to infiltrate their base
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:27.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,and save my friends from the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.46,0:14:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor. Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How did they know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.47,0:14:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.57,0:15:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Shocker commander-in-chief,\NAmbassador Hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.34,0:15:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,has come here to escort\Nyou personally, Doctor Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, won't you get in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Your resistance is futile.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.76,0:15:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.68,0:15:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a close look at that\Ncable car, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown your true colors at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:15:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw through my disguise?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi...\NYou underestimate Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.28,0:16:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't leave here alive this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.32,0:16:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall! Fall to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.67,0:17:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.17,0:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Doctor Kihara and Taki\Nto our base at Horai Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think of the view?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I find it comparable\Nto America's Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That tall, thin mountain will serve\Nas Shocker's broadcast antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.36,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't help you undermine\NJapanese communications!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough talking tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll come around soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.80,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for the execution.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Execution?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.42,0:18:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All who oppose Shocker must die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.64,0:19:00.51,Italics,,0,0,0,,If I die here, everything I've\Ndone will be for naught.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:04.75,Italics,,0,0,0,,I have to go... I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... look closely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.51,0:19:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki. Was Hongo really killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.90,0:19:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If he'd survived, he'd be here by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we really going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm too young to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Push them into the ravine, one at a time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just forgive them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.85,0:19:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore him. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Kihara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not bend to Shocker threats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Rider?\NShow yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.41,0:20:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward... show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.26,0:20:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.89,0:20:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Abugomes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- You came!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rider!\N- Rider, save Doctor Kihara!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.82,0:20:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Good luck out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.74,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Knee Block!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:18.90,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground\Nwith a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:26.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.42,0:20:30.17,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:33.83,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:07.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tearing through the\Nair with a Rider Plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.50,0:21:14.21,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great flight that\Nskates over the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:18.71,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up tornadoes with a Rider Jet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:22.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.42,0:21:26.26,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.26,0:21:29.94,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:52.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Swimming through the\Noceans with a Rider Swim,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:59.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,a great dive flitting through the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.07,0:22:03.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Calling up whirlpools with a Rider Screw!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:07.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Dragging enemies down with a Rider Lung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.42,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.42,0:22:15.49,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.50,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, Shocker's plan has failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad. I truly am...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll get you back, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.94,0:22:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.23,0:22:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about us?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Arima Hot Springs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take a nice rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.05,0:22:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.77,0:22:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad we came.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.45,0:22:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do we get down from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.01,0:22:58.23,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider's deathmatch with\NShocker at Mount Rokko in Arima
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:59.97,Narrator,,0,0,0,,ended with justice prevailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker would target Japan\Nwith their evil once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.28,0:23:07.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Fight on, Hongo Takeshi,\Nthe Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.07,0:23:10.84,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.39,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(315.175,252.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:14.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I am the blood-sucking monster Mosquilas!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.94,0:23:18.01,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I was sent from South\NAmerica to kill Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.01,0:23:21.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,I'll kill Rider this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:23.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and throw him into the\Nplunge pool of Nachi Falls!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Next time, "The Blood-Sucking\NMosquilas Versus the Two Riders."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.74,0:23:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It'll be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs115\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,730.389)}The Blood-Sucking Mosquilas \NVersus the Two Riders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.85,0:23:40.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.25,0:23:43.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.30,0:23:45.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.18,0:23:48.24,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.60,0:23:52.52,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.52,0:23:54.29,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.29,0:23:55.82,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.12,0:23:58.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.22,0:24:03.92,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:07.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.48,0:24:11.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:15.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The Mount Rokko Pursuit of\Nthe Monstrous Abugomes!